{"type": "article", "id": 52824, "title": "造型巧妙的衣帽架，换个造型就是晾衣架｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-05-03T23:00:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 8925, "name": "Moooi"}, {"id": 49907, "name": "Arte"}, {"id": 15888, "name": "本土创造"}, {"id": 49908, "name": "Hardgraft"}, {"id": 28346, "name": "Joseph Joseph"}, {"id": 49909, "name": "Etain Ho"}, {"id": 49910, "name": "Omayra Maymo"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 119, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180503223940cmRKENhLnH9kap7P.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; min-height: 13.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 11.0px 0.0px; line-height: 18.0px; font: 16.2px Times; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; min-height: 19.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} span.s5 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #e36c09; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #e36c09} span.s7 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s8 {font-kerning: none; color: #545454; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #545454} span.s9 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #545454; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #545454} span.s10 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Brwise Cap Collecting Bottle Opener by Joseph Joseph</h3><p>喝酒本该是一件解忧、尽兴且雅致的活动，但开瓶盖的步骤却让很多人犯了难。英国厨具品牌 Joseph Joseph 推出的 Brwise 系列，解决了不少包括鸡尾酒、红酒的开瓶难题，这款可收集瓶盖的创意开瓶器，是其专门针对啤酒瓶提出的解决方案。开瓶之后最多可收集 16 个瓶盖，透明窗设计，也方便统计自己的战绩，挺有趣的设计。售价 67 元，<a href=\"https://www.amazon.cn/Joseph-20090-BarWise-Cap-Collecting-Catcher/dp/B01KOGAFNQ/ref=sr_1_1?tag=geo-23&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1510748356&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=barwise&amp;th=1\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224013torbHqSTy7OpdhCI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.803810\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224013QTrERugZOMIaid2A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224014t3uHX08Uif59SkLs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.769524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224012ySPR3dYHL1EJlhNA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.802857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224012ZNYcpVkeLTy5EgAB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.802857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>SPORT IPAD MINI CASE . CLASSIC by Hardgraft</h3><p>来自伦敦的皮革品牌 Hard Graft 一直以精工著名，品牌设计涵盖包袋、行李袋、钱夹、电脑包和行李箱等。这款 SPORT IPAD 迷你保护套，也可以作为支架使用。它由毛毡制成，触感很好，且有极佳的防护性能。四个铆钉将皮质配件固定在保护套上，折叠固定即可变身为支架，方便实用。售价 80 欧元，<a href=\"https://www.hardgraft.com/products/snapipadmini-classic\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224040EoJgaeyOpiMSckUN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805032240411EmrwyQzUMWpPXVC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224041OpI8Ssi9Kz2oAnhu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224041dCSIY1k9bLqN2xnh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224042EVljhHgu19BfNKvy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224042YHMji0z6yGZBRkhS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>水泥装饰墙砖·六系列 by 本土创造</h3><p>广州设计品牌本土创造将陶瓷废渣与混凝土相结合制作墙砖。这套“六”系列的水泥装饰墙砖，以混凝土和废弃陶瓷为成分，一体出模而成，表面细腻平滑，轻薄坚固。</p><p>在设计上，运用光影成像原理，在二维的几何画面上打造三维立体效果，极具装饰性和艺术性。在此基础上，“六”既能实现环保意义，又能将瓷砖废渣转化为极具使用价值，能批量生产的产品，甚至形成可持续发展的产业。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224357XYC37gbo4qa5lJ8S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.694792\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224357GF91f4oW8xVpkYLM.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224411n7xTyZRoiUCf2Vel.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224406BhQCIXwx6yGoK8Hl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.694792\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Museum of Extinct Animals by Moooi</h3><p>米兰设计周期间，荷兰设计品牌 Moooi 与比利时品牌 Arte 合作，推出一系列新型壁纸，以灭绝的动物为主题。设计师的灵感源自 10 种已灭绝的动物，包括渡渡鸟、伞型乌贼、红脸树獭以及长须美洲豹等等。</p><p>Moooi 通过探索各种博物馆的藏品发现了这些动物的图像，“我们搜遍了世界各地的博物馆，并找到了令人难以置信的动物图画，”Moooi 联合创始人 Marcel Wanders 说。“许多东西都消失了，只能生活在我们的回忆和想象中。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224501hceqywfxF1v30ENV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224504guQ9UBFPwm57CsoK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.629865\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224505yJvbSIwCWHUsqLQ0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.145002\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224511npGy6MoBJiH0KaIU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.059554\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805032245092H9f5M0gje6WQuzn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.308799\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224512UrZ8nRzfSC0AToDK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224515d5rGnKJ0XM4o2Nzx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.786802\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/05/03/moooi-arte-wallpaper-museum-extinct-animals-milan-design-week/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Swappi cart by Omayra Maymo</h3><p>英国家具电商网站 <a href=\"http://made.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">made.com</a> 最近推出一款名为 Swappi 的众筹产品。这是丹麦设计师 Omayra Maymo 推出的针对传统抽屉柜的替代解决方案。</p><p>Swappi 不仅能够提供存储、收纳功能，可调节的抽屉也能变为展示型货架。手推车的形式更适合小型空间使用，轻松实现在房间里四处移动的需求。薄荷绿色的框架搭配四个木制格挡，更适合当代家居空间。早鸟价 279 英镑，<a href=\"https://www.made.com/talentlab/shop/launch-collection/swappi-cart-mint-green-and-ash/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224726Gi4mhO5FnVNUWlgt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805032247263CjlpGMbxezN4DaP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224726VFg42R9CPXSAGQ0T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224727paMg4Gtbr9jNDnOB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Yiliy Coat Stand by Etain Ho</h3><p>这同样是一款来自 <a href=\"http://made.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">made.com</a> 的众筹产品。Yiliy 衣架的设计构想来自伦敦设计师 Etain Ho。黑色粉末涂层钢架搭配混凝土底座。</p><p>除了悬挂大衣和帽子之外，还可以将一根钢管从基座里拿出，在两个 V 形支架之间架起一根横杆，将其转变为晾衣杆使用。早鸟价 104 英镑，<a href=\"https://www.made.com/talentlab/shop/launch-collection/yiliy-coat-stand-grey-and-black/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224758fDuaohOwcylHPx2C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224759UNBFxY4Ejzv7IH0u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224759gaw1zsjbSmqR03DJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180503224759fevITKxUSoQXd9Mb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}